rence-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.teara.govt.nz/en/cook-islanders/2/3\">Cook Islanders - Haircutting ceremony, Porirua - Te Ara Encyclopedia of New Zealand</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.teara.govt.nz/en/niueans/1/6\">Niueans - A young Niuean at his hair-cutting ceremony - Te Ara Encyclopedia of New Zealand</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=First_haircut&amp;action=edit&amp;section=17\" title=\"Edit section: External links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.hairarchives.com/private/haircutnew.htm\">The First Haircut</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.sunsetbeacon.com/archives/richmondreview/2005editions/Jun05/ChineseTraditions.html\">Family Celebrations at Heart  of Many Chinese Traditions</a></li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw2277\nCached time: 20180921181933\nCache expiry: 1900800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.268 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.358 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 477/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1500000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 24739/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 5949/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 2/500\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 4164/5000000 bytes\nNumber of Wikibase entities loaded: 0/400\nLua time usage: 0.182/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 10.06 MB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  321.842      1 -